Identify an ML problem
•	Recommendation of videos on TIKTOK for fresh users.
Classify the ML type
•	It’s Reforcement Learning algorithm because it doesn’t have a data or information about the user. So they learn through by recommend random video to user and see if the user :
	 Tap the button of like
	Tap the button of follow
	Tap the button copy link
	Watch hour of the video, etc..
Outline the ML work flow
1.	Recommend random video based on the local environment 
2.	See the user reaction(like, follow, watch hour, copy link, etc.…..)
3.	Learn the information from the last 5 videos
4.	Based on the information recommend videos
Identify one possible failure point
Bad Evaluation: by keeping the user data recorded and make sure the data of quality.
